---
layout: base.njk
title: Session Logs
breadcrumb: "Sessions"
---

<p><em>A record of every adventure undertaken, every choice made, every scar earned. The chronicle does not forget.</em></p>

<div class="ornament">· · ·</div>

<ul class="session-list">
{% for session in collections.sessions %}
  <li>
    <span class="s-date">{{ session.date | readableDate }}</span>
    <a href="{{ session.url }}">{{ session.data.title }}</a>
    {% if session.data.description %}
    <div class="s-desc">{{ session.data.description }}</div>
    {% endif %}
  </li>
{% else %}
  <li><em>No sessions recorded yet. The adventure begins soon...</em></li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
